{"tid":1703203,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"傻既都諗到聽朝黨鐵站一定有狗車佈定防，咁要點應對呢？得一個方法","createTime":"2019-11-10T07:14:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T07:22:02.000Z","uid":161430,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"38e6274d820bf19e0ffb0ea38269f8c22bfc716f","tid":1703203,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T07:14:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唯一方法就係人夠多，冇其他<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n人少 = 成堆豬籠喺黨鐵站外 vs 人少少望住個telegram喺側邊black bloc等埋位既你 = 失鳩敗 = 最後你會死上連登發悔氣話冇人呀<br />\n<br />\n人少 = 你set零零丁丁既roadblock，都唔駛狗，司機都幫你清左個roadblock走啦，到時又唔肯噴巴士因為驚唔好睇 =  失鳩敗<br />\n<br />\n人少 = 入到站想塞鐵變撚左正常咁搭鐵，返埋公司都未有事發生 =  失鳩敗<br />\n<br />\n聽日只得一個方法可以贏，就係朝早都準時齊人，人多，冇其他<br />\n人唔多，討論咩方法都冇用，聽日早起身一次，周圍都係人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"623bdc81b02f11a7bee4b4b53204033de20b3938","tid":1703203,"uid":32220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T07:16:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4324183d0c1dc64b1480fe971ba750074f1e9a64","tid":1703203,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T07:16:22.000Z","msg":"早起身一次，準時一次，<br />\n唔好做自私撚<br />\n朝早望定網上消息"},{"pid":"452f4bcbbf4e45d852e32dc7dcb33ba1a7826948","tid":1703203,"uid":82640,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T07:19:13.000Z","msg":"其實各大露天路軌加一嚿磚已經停駛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n建議警方沿線派人組成人鏈<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hMECjPc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhMECjPc.jpg&h=1d02198b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3911bd46d6e999bc38c4c2f402cb17ff3cc7c9dd","tid":1703203,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T07:20:03.000Z","msg":"見大家熱烈討論聽朝<br />\n有好多方法係work<br />\n但令件事最唔work既就係冇人手<br />\n而之前朝早搞活動既往績係9成9會冇人出<br />\n話7點，睇怕聽朝都要到8點先有人<br />\n<br />\n想成事既一定要早起身 準時一次出現係集會地點附近 夠人<br />\n否則真係講乜都冇用"},{"pid":"fdc1019d422d79817d71571c725f1bb41f503d67","tid":1703203,"uid":194298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T07:20:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔好明顯阻鐵，但唔覺意唔小心唔舒服等等，有狗都吹你唔脹</span>"},{"pid":"d1806b0578c8b083a09370b20aecb662d94ae0c5","tid":1703203,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T07:20:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>見大家熱烈討論聽朝<br />\n有好多方法係work<br />\n但令件事最唔work既就係冇人手<br />\n而之前朝早搞活動既往績係9成9會冇人出<br />\n話7點，睇怕聽朝都要到8點先有人<br />\n<br />\n想成事既一定要早起身 準時一次出現係集<del>會</del>合地點附近 夠人<br />\n否則真係講乜都冇用</blockquote>"},{"pid":"3dc9a696a9ba7b211d71482e3a5f7e3fe8c4b19b","tid":1703203,"uid":220008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T07:21:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d62eba612e80a7ef2487e742872511042596da06","tid":1703203,"uid":42629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fdc1019d422d79817d71571c725f1bb41f503d67","tid":1703203,"uid":194298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T07:20:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔好明顯阻鐵，但唔覺意唔小心唔舒服等等，有狗都吹你唔脹</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T07:22:02.000Z","msg":"唔舒服都當你塞鐵啦聽日，除非你係40以上"}]}